Package: rblocksync3
Architecture: all
Depends: ${python3:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, python3, openssh-client
Description: Remote block-level file synchronization tool
 rblocksync3 is a Python tool for efficient file synchronization using
 block-level hashing. It transfers only the changed blocks between files/devices,
 making it ideal for synchronizing large files or VM images over SSH connections.
 .
 Features:
  - Block-level synchronization
  - Keeps zeroes blocks for lvm-thin devices or sparse files
  - Remote and local file support
  - Multi-threaded scanning and transfers
  - SSH-based remote operations